Login Azure Console -> Search Bar -> Virtual machines -> Select The Virtual machines -> Create -> Virtual machine -> Select The Resource group -> 
Virtual machine name -> Name -> Username -> Name -> SSH public key source(Select The Use existing key stored in Azure) -> Stored Keys(Select The Key Pair) -> 
Public inbound ports(None) -> Go To Networking Tab -> NIC network security group(Select The Advanced) -> Configure network security group(Select The Security Group) -> 
Select The Option Delete public IP and NIC when VM is deleted -> Go To Advanced Tab > -> Custom data -> Copy And Paste The instance-setup-script -> 
Go To Review + create Tab -> Create
